---
// src/components/Studio.astro
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="font-body font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
    <p class="font-body text-lg text-[var(--text-color)]/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Wise Goose Games is a two-person indie studio based in California.
    </p>
    <p class="font-body text-lg text-[var(--text-color)]/80 leading-relaxed">
      We make games because we believe puzzles should feel like conversations, not chores.
      Every mechanic is placed with intention. Every level is hand-crafted.
      No procedural filler, no artificial padding. Just honest design.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
